highlights.text: Diego Mitre has the most spots on Viral Songs South Korea. “To the Infinity Castle - Muzan vs Hashira Theme (from "Demon Slayer") - Cover” is the highest at #2.
“おつかれSUMMER” by HALCALI has been on Viral Songs South Korea the longest, at 119 days straight.
“Typing” by 樊宇镈(Coulson Fan) is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs South Korea, up 29 spots at #58.
“Akaza's Requiem” by James Liam Figueroa is the highest new entry on Viral Songs South Korea at #66.
